.TH vdf_parse 3

.SH NAME
vdf_parse

.SH LIBRARY
Valve Data Format Parser Library (libvdfc)

.SH SYNOPSIS
#include <vdfc/vdf.h>

VDFcode vdf_parse(const char *buffer, VDFNode **out);

.SH DESCRIPTION
Parse a VDF buffer into a node tree.
the tree must be released with vdf_free_node().

.SH RETURN VALUE
Upon a successful read, returns \fB`VDF_OK`\fR.
Otherwise, returns an error code.

.SH ERRORS
.PP
\fB`VDF_ERR_PARSE`\fR: Malformed VDF content.
.PP
\fB`VDF_ERR_MALLOC`\fR: Memory allocation failure.

